This research examines user reactions and perceptions to emotional or sentimentally manipulative goodbye messages from AI companions. More precisely, it addresses how those messages influence user attitudes toward the AI, retention of using the app, perceptions of corporate social responsibility, and the willingness to recommend or warn others about the app.
